================================================================================

INSTALLATION
------------

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES
------------

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

[#:for (name,ver) in props/depends]
    [#name][#:if ver gt 0] v[#ver][#:end if]
[#:end for]

